00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:28.000
<v Father>
You young couple just carry on. Take no notice of me … [action] (silence; they smile half-heartedly) I don't want to feel as though I'm getting in the way.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
<v Carol>
Oh no dad, you're not.

